  "top10": {
    "introHtml": "<p>Refreshed 2026-07-07. Scanned 85 raw listings across Cars.com (27), CarGurus (21), and AutoTrader (37). After filtering 2-seat roadsters (Miata, SL-Class, Boxster, Z4, etc.), 46 4-seat convertibles remain. 100% image coverage across all sources. 4 Mercedes SL-Class (2-seat roadsters) filtered from Cars.com (27 raw). 2-seat roadsters and non-convertible body styles filtered from AutoTrader (37 raw). TrueCar skipped per task config (body-style filter broken). Note: 2010 Ford Mustang (Reading, PA) appeared in Cars.com results but measured 40mi \u2014 excluded. 1 qualifying 2005+ Mustang found within radius.</p>",
    "picks": [
      {
        "rank": 1,
        "year": 2011,
        "make": "Audi",
        "model": "A5",
        "trim": "2.0T Premium Plus Convertible",
        "price": 9990,
        "mileage": 56654,
        "location": "Trevose, PA",
        "distanceMi": 27,
        "dealer": "Divan Auto Group",
        "source": "autotrader",
        "url": "https://www.autotrader.com/cars-for-sale/vehicle/784924266",
        "dealRating": "Good Deal",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.autotrader.com/hn/c/00a43b75d37e448fb52a3aec3ca1b098.jpg",
        "whyGood": "The B8 Audi A5 Cabriolet is the budget MVP of this search \u2014 56k miles on a 4-seat drop-top with a strong 2.0T and quattro AWD for just $9,990 is exceptional value. A5 Cabriolets are rare and hold their shape well. Good Deal badge validates the price.",
        "whatToVerify": "Full convertible top cycle (open AND close, watch for hesitation or rattles). Check headliner and rear carpet for water stains \u2014 a telltale of top-seal failure. Inspect rear window seam. Pull timing chain service history (B8 2.0T is chain-driven but tensioner should be inspected at this mileage). MMI screen and electronics check.",
        "bottomLine": "Best-value 4-seat convertible in the search \u2014 low mileage, AWD, and a modern platform for under $10k."
      },
      {
        "rank": 2,
        "year": 2010,
        "make": "BMW",
        "model": "328i",
        "trim": "Convertible",
        "price": 10900,
        "mileage": 80232,
        "location": "West Chester, PA",
        "distanceMi": 9,
        "dealer": "Sky Motor Cars",
        "source": "cargurus",
        "url": "https://www.cargurus.com/details/451367312",
        "dealRating": null,
        "imageUrl": "https://static.cargurus.com/images/forsale/2026/06/20/14/22/2010_bmw_3_series-pic-2956539671150296942-1024x768.jpeg",
        "whyGood": "The E93 328i is the gold standard of sub-$15k convertibles \u2014 balanced rear-wheel-drive chassis, 230hp inline-6, proper 4 seats, and a hydraulic soft top that's mature and reliable by 2010. Only 9 miles from Media at a proper dealer.",
        "whatToVerify": "N52 engine oil leaks (valve cover gasket, oil filter housing). Soft-top hydraulic rams (look for slow close or fluid on the pump). Rear window de-fog function. Check for cooling system work (thermostat, water pump). Water staining on rear seat leather from top seam.",
        "bottomLine": "The right car for the right money \u2014 close, reliable platform, and a genuinely fun drive."
      },
      {
        "rank": 3,
        "year": 2015,
        "make": "MINI",
        "model": "Convertible",
        "trim": "Cooper",
        "price": 9999,
        "mileage": 55000,
        "location": "Easttown, PA",
        "distanceMi": 8,
        "dealer": null,
        "source": "cars.com",
        "url": "https://www.cars.com/vehicledetail/c73c9af6-32ed-4289-b16b-fab9b3e278b1/",
        "dealRating": null,
        "imageUrl": "https://platform.cstatic-images.com/large/in/v2/p2p/7c218327-0c22-43ec-ba78-96ef5e726111/519f581a-e182-4041-9b51-5ef13606b3b4.jpg",
        "whyGood": "Newest convertible in the top 10 by a wide margin \u2014 2015 F57 platform with only 55k miles, clean title and no accidents confirmed, and just 8 miles away in Easttown. Fun around-town character with surprising top-down presence.",
        "whatToVerify": "Full top cycle test (MINI cloth tops can develop window separation). Check rear seat headroom and access. Verify no recalled items outstanding. MINI reliability varies \u2014 check service records for timing chain tensioner (prince-era engines had issues, F57 should be cleaner).",
        "bottomLine": "Closest, newest, cleanest pick \u2014 great for someone who wants a no-drama fun daily drop-top."
      },
      {
        "rank": 4,
        "year": 2004,
        "make": "BMW",
        "model": "645Ci",
        "trim": "Convertible",
        "price": 11000,
        "mileage": 51000,
        "location": "Chester, PA",
        "distanceMi": 5,
        "dealer": "Private Seller Exchange",
        "source": "autotrader",
        "url": "https://www.autotrader.com/cars-for-sale/vehicle/784809537",
        "dealRating": null,
        "imageUrl": "https://assets.cai-media-management.com/ps-vehicle-media/d0a40452-8b6b-4d92-b80d-00e8c61292b7.jpeg",
        "whyGood": "51,000 miles on a V8 E64 grand tourer convertible for $11k is almost suspiciously good. The 645Ci is one of BMW's best-looking cars ever made, with real 4-seat space and 325hp N62 V8 thunder. Only 5 miles from Media.",
        "whatToVerify": "N62 engine VANOS unit inspection and valve stem seals (known oil consumer). Check for SMG or standard auto \u2014 prefer the 6-speed auto (GA6HP26). Soft-top hydraulics full cycle test. IBS (intelligent battery sensor) and electrical gremlins \u2014 bring a ISTA-capable scanner. Verify why mileage is so low at 22 years old.",
        "bottomLine": "V8 grand tourer at a steal \u2014 stunning looks and real performance, but demands careful pre-purchase inspection."
      },
      {
        "rank": 5,
        "year": 2012,
        "make": "Ford",
        "model": "Mustang",
        "trim": "V6 Convertible RWD",
        "price": 10995,
        "mileage": 96539,
        "location": "West Chester, PA",
        "distanceMi": 12,
        "dealer": "Jonathan's Auto Outlet",
        "source": "cargurus",
        "url": "https://www.cargurus.com/details/445737422",
        "dealRating": null,
        "imageUrl": "https://static.cargurus.com/images/forsale/2026/04/30/14/23/2012_ford_mustang-pic-2949931544508764713-1024x768.jpeg",
        "whyGood": "The S197 Mustang V6 is the most bulletproof fun-car engine in this search \u2014 the 305hp Cyclone V6 launched Ford's reliability renaissance and routinely hits 200k+ miles. Convertible body with proper rear seat. Well under $11k in West Chester.",
        "whatToVerify": "Full top cycle \u2014 S197 tops are mechanical and durable but check the latch mechanism and weather seal. Rear seat water staining from top seal. Check 8.8 rear axle for clunk on takeoff (common, often needs fluid). Rocker rust inspection underneath.",
        "bottomLine": "The no-nonsense fun-car pick \u2014 proven powertrain, easy to maintain, American V6 sound that won't quit."
      },
      {
        "rank": 6,
        "year": 2011,
        "make": "Volvo",
        "model": "C70",
        "trim": "T5",
        "price": 9990,
        "mileage": 93899,
        "location": "Vineland, NJ",
        "distanceMi": 35,
        "dealer": "JC Miller Auto Sales",
        "source": "cargurus",
        "url": "https://www.cargurus.com/details/446981957",
        "dealRating": null,
        "imageUrl": "https://static.cargurus.com/images/forsale/2026/05/01/19/22/2011_volvo_c70-pic-5280690002271591302-1024x768.jpeg",
        "whyGood": "The C70 retractable hardtop is a head-turner with no soft-top worries \u2014 the folding roof mechanism is elegant and robust by 2011. Swedish-built T5 five-cylinder turbo has real character. At 93k miles and $9,990 with a clean, quiet personality.",
        "whatToVerify": "Full roof cycle (open, close, emergency release test). Check all hydraulic seals on the roof mechanism \u2014 leaks are costly. Inspect roof drains (front and rear) for blockage. T5 timing belt service history (critical \u2014 should be done by ~100k). Check for P0016/P0017 cam correlation codes.",
        "bottomLine": "The sophisticated choice \u2014 a retractable hardtop grand tourer with Scandinavian style at a solid price."
      },
      {
        "rank": 7,
        "year": 2016,
        "make": "Buick",
        "model": "Cascada",
        "trim": "Premium FWD",
        "price": 11195,
        "mileage": 71211,
        "location": "Sewell, NJ",
        "distanceMi": 25,
        "dealer": "Automotive Avenues of Sewell",
        "source": "cargurus",
        "url": "https://www.cargurus.com/details/449886715",
        "dealRating": null,
        "imageUrl": "https://static.cargurus.com/images/forsale/2026/07/03/22/42/2016_buick_cascada-pic-994318415939501030-1024x768.jpeg",
        "whyGood": "The Cascada is the most underrated 4-seat convertible in America \u2014 Opel-engineered, genuinely well-built, and at 71k miles on a 2016 it's comparatively fresh. Premium trim means heated leather, navigation, and a Bose stereo. Lots of car for $11,195.",
        "whatToVerify": "Full top operation \u2014 Cascada electric roofs are quiet but check for hesitation. Roof drain tubes (front corners) \u2014 confirm no standing water in trunk. Verify no airbag/TPMS warning lights. Check for any GM technical service bulletins on the 1.6T engine (turbo actuator).",
        "bottomLine": "The overlooked gem \u2014 refined, spacious, and properly modern for a 2016 convertible at this price."
      },
      {
        "rank": 8,
        "year": 2013,
        "make": "Mercedes-Benz",
        "model": "E-Class",
        "trim": "E 350 Cabriolet",
        "price": 11995,
        "mileage": 119433,
        "location": "Spring City, PA",
        "distanceMi": 20,
        "dealer": "Premier Motor Group",
        "source": "cars.com",
        "url": "https://www.cars.com/vehicledetail/168e7196-5cc3-49bb-8faf-622353175793/",
        "dealRating": null,
        "imageUrl": "https://platform.cstatic-images.com/large/in/v2/687e2a1f-ebc7-5430-89f7-b9a52e6185f9/f3f63d52-5d12-42b0-98bb-b1240058acd8/aOEatydVFsvUrrSZ9U83SKz6byo.jpg",
        "whyGood": "The A207 E350 Cabriolet is arguably the most beautiful car in this entire search \u2014 proper 4-seat grand touring, 3.5L V6, and a folding soft top with acoustic roof lining. Clean title and no accidents verified through Cars.com. At $11,995 it's as close to aspirational as this budget gets.",
        "whatToVerify": "Top mechanism full cycle (look for roof-module codes). Check all four roof drains \u2014 blocked drains cause water in the trunk and footwells. Interior for water staining. Mercedes maintenance costs at this mileage (120k+ service). Check for ABC suspension warning lights if equipped.",
        "bottomLine": "The grand touring pick \u2014 genuinely stunning, genuinely roomy, genuinely expensive to maintain if anything goes wrong."
      },
      {
        "rank": 9,
        "year": 2013,
        "make": "BMW",
        "model": "328i",
        "trim": "Convertible",
        "price": 8326,
        "mileage": 144928,
        "location": "Gilbertsville, PA",
        "distanceMi": 29,
        "dealer": "Josie's Auto Sales",
